(343, 'DK-IND-02', 'CL-DK-IND-01', 'BU-3', 'Tax on HFCs, PFCs and SF6', 'Reduction of industrial gas emissions (HFC, PFC, SF6)', 'Taxes corresponding to their GWP have been imposed on each of the greenhouse gases from March 2001 in combination with the Danish CO2 tax of DKK 0.1 per kg CO2. This means that HFC-134a is subject to a tax of DKK 130/kg, as it has a GWP of 1,300. There is a ceiling of DKK 400/kg so although SF6 has a GWP of 23,900, the tax is only DKK 400/kg and not DKK 2,390/ kg. The tax is imposed on the substances on importation because none of them are produced in Denmark.', '2001', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'CL-DK-IND-01', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'DenmarksUpdateOnPAMsAndProjections-15march 2007, p.63', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
