(464, 'ES-ENS-03', NULL, '25', 'Directive 2004/8/EC concerning the promotion of cogeneration (RD 616/2007 concerning the promotion of cogeneration).', 'Promotion of cogeneration in order to reduce CO2 and other substances', 'This regulation intends to establish a common transparent market to promote and facilitate the installation of cogeneration centres in places with existing or foreseable heat demand. In the short term, the Directive shall consolidate existing installations for cogeneration and promote new centres. Int the mid and long term, the Directive shall create a necessary market for efficient cogeneration in order to reduce CO2 emissions and other substances and to contribute to sustainable development.', '2006', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', 'Reduction of SOx, NOx, TSP', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(465, 'ES-TRA-01', NULL, '26', 'Directive 2003/30/EC concerning the promotion of the utilisation of biofuels and other renewable fuels in transportation. (RD 61/2006)', 'Promotion usage of biofuels and other renewable fuels.', 'The measure intends that biofuels (liquid or gaseous combustibles used in transport and bulk commodities, originating from biomass, i.e. residuals and biodegradable residuals from inter alia agriculture and forestry) represent a minimal percentage of commercial fuels.', '2006', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', 'Its impact differs subject to contaminants and is not clearly quantified.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(466, 'ES-TRA-02', NULL, '27', 'Directives 70/220/EC concerning light vehicle emissions (last modification 98/69) and 88/77/EC concerning heavy vehicles (last modification 1999/96) (RD 2028/1986 y sus modificaciones)', 'Limit emissions from petrol and diesel vehicles', 'These Directives apply to exhaust gas, evaporation and oil sump emissions and the longevity of anticontamination equipment of explosive motor vehicles as well as exhaust gas emissions and the durability of anticontamination equipment of compression motor vehicles of the classes M1 and N1 except vehicles of the category N1.', '2006', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', 'Reductions of  CO, NOx, TSP, HC', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
