(473, 'ES-CRS-02', NULL, '34', 'Strategy for energy saving and efficiency in Spain 2004-2012, Action plan 2005-2007 and Action plan 2008-2012.', 'Promote a sustainable energy policy which guarantees supply, maintains competitiveness and reduces environmental impact.', 'The strategy identifies strategic objectives as well as the path which energy policy should take in order to achieve its objectives: security in quantity supply and price with threshold levels of self-sufficiency, taking into account the environmental impact of its use and the important component relative to the competitiveness of our economy.', '2006', NULL, '2696', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Change in activity data (energy savings)', 'Yes', 'COMUNICACI&Oacute;N DE ESPA&Ntilde;A A LA COMISI&Oacute;N EUROPEA, ART&Iacute;CULO 3.2. (a), (b), (c) y (d) DE LA DECISI&Oacute;N 280/2004/CE', NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', 'Reduces other contaminants at including reduction measures of fuel consumption and improves energy efficiency.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
