(478, 'ES-ENS-06', NULL, '39', 'National Plan for Strategic Carbon Reserve 2006-2012 and New Model of Integrated and Sustainable Development of Mining Areas', 'Arrange carbon mining in Spain', 'This plan arranges carbon mining, taking into account social and regional aspects as well as the need to maintain a determinated native carbon production, which allows to guarantee the access to reserves. Furthermore, it aims to mitigate the impact of sectoral job losses by promoting the creation of alternative employment to monoculture of carbon through support of entrepreneurial projects which create jobs, potentiation of human resources of the mining areas by financing training activities and infrastructure.', '2006', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', 'Affects emissions of combustion gases in relation to other cleaner fuels.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
