(492, 'ES-AGR-05', NULL, '53', 'Plan for the reduction of nitrogen fertiliser use', 'Decrease the utilisation of nitrogen fertilisers in order to reduce emissions of N2O,NH3 and Nox.', 'This measure intends to introduce new fertiliser types, to improve its use and efficienct utilisation, as well as to incorporate dung and liquid manure complementarily to synthetic nitrogen fertilisers. Moreover, it establishes control and regulation programmes for mechanical equipment of dung distributors and support for the introduction of equipment for the application of these fertilisers.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', 'Reduces NH3 and Nox.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(493, 'ES-IND-20', NULL, '54', 'Voluntary agreement SF6', 'Decrease SF6 emissions of electric high tension equipment in transmission and distribution grids as means of arc isolation and extinction.', 'The voluntary agreement between producers and users of this equipment, including the Plan for Urgent Measures of the EECCEL, intends to decrease SF6 emissions, basically due to the following actions.<br />? Immprove the formation of persons who undertake the reparation, maintenance, fabrication and assembling of the equipment.<br />? Fabrication and use of equipment with low emission rates.<br />? Supply of environmental information to end-users in gas extraction, recovery and recycling.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(494, 'ES-IND-21', NULL, '55', 'Voluntary agreement PFCs', 'Reduction of PFC.', 'This agreement includes a voluntary compromise on the reduction of PFCs with a company dedicated to aluminium production.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(495, 'ES-ENC-05', NULL, '56', 'Registry of voluntary compromises of companies', 'Reduction of the comsumption of energy and greenhouse gases in business.', 'This measure intends to create a publicly accessable registry of voluntary compromises of companies on the comsumption of energy and greenhouse gases.<br />The emission reduction which is expected as a consequence of this measure was redivided between the electricity generating sector and the road transport sector.<br />Firstly, the decrease emerges from utilised combustibles in electricity generation (due to reduced electricity consumption of companies which signed these voluntary compromises). Secondly, the mobility decrease of private vehicles.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', 'This measure will reduce other contaminants in relation to sectors which sign voluntary agreements.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(496, 'ES-TRA-07', NULL, '57', 'Course of action in mobility: promotion of higher booking ratios', 'Increase of the booking ratios of road transport vehicles.', 'This measure intends to optimise the booking ratios of road transport vehicles (passenger cars and autobuses) in order to decrease emissions of the transport sector, urban as well as interurban ones.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', 'This measure results in significant reductions of other contaminants like Nox, COVNM, TSP, CO&hellip;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(497, 'ES-TRA-08', NULL, '58', 'Restriction on the road traffic of private vehicles in  city centres (in effect in cities with high density of urban road traffic).', 'Limit the mobility of private transport in centres of big cities.', 'This measure intends to restrict the mobility of private transport in centres of big cities and respective commuting, by transferring this mobility towards more efficient modes of transport as railway.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', 'This measure results in significant reductions of other contaminants like Nox, COVNM, TSP, CO&hellip;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(498, 'ES-ENC-06', NULL, '59', 'Courses of action in buildings (limitation of internal/external illumination hours. CCAA and local entities).', 'Reduction of electricty consumption in the tertiary sector (offices, general administration buildings of the state, hospitals, sports facilities, commercial centres, etc.)', 'It is estimatd that the application of this measure might achieve electricity savings in illumination, which implies a reduction of combustibles in electricity generation by conventional thermal.A gradual implementation of this measure till 2020 is supposed.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', 'Owing to achieved energy saving this measure results in reduction of contaminants generated by electricity generation, liek Nox, Sox, TSP, CO,&hellip;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(499, 'ES-ENC-07', NULL, '60', 'Improve energy efficiency in buildings across improvements in protective insulation and saving management', 'Improve energy efficiency in buildings.', 'This measure could affect the tertiary commercial and institutional sector. Its application might achieve savings in fuel consumption of the tertiary commercial and instutional sector as well as savings in electricity consumption for thermal purposes, which translates into a reduction of fuel consumption in electriciy generation.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', 'Owing to achieved energy saving this measure results in reduction of contaminants generated by electricity generation, liek Nox, Sox, TSP, CO,&hellip;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(500, 'ES-ENC-08', NULL, '61', 'Control of internal temperature systems in commercial centres and offices (private) by avoiding losses through windows and doors.', 'Energy saving in climatisation of the tertiary sector.', 'The commercial sector comprises 22% of energy consumption of the tertiary sector. Moreover, in big commercial centres about 100% of energy consumption is electric. This measure focuses only on losses by climatisation and involves saving in electricity consumption.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', 'Owing to achieved energy saving this measure results in reduction of contaminants generated by electricity generation, liek Nox, Sox, TSP, CO,&hellip;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(501, 'ES-ENC-09', NULL, '62', 'Substitution of present illumination by low consumption electric bulbs in the private sector.', 'Potentitation of low consumption illumination systems.', 'The measure intends to subsitute the present electric bulbs by low consumption lamps.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', 'Owing to achieved energy saving this measure results in reduction of contaminants generated by electricity generation, liek Nox, Sox, TSP, CO,&hellip;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(502, 'ES-ENC-10', NULL, '63', 'Utilisation of thermal solar panels at a higher percentage than in the Action Plan of the E4 2008-2012 in existing public buildings.', 'Promotion of thermal solar panels for sanitary hot water in public buildings.', 'Public buildings (hospitals, education centres and sports centres) comprise 15% of total energy consumption in the tertiary sector. In the year 2000, hospitals accounted for 11% of total consumption (50% fuels and 50% electricity), education centres for 4%, (69% fuels and 31% electricity) and sports centres for a very small percentage which is included in the education centres (with swimming pool: 55% fuels and 45% electricity; without swimming pool: 80% and 20%, respectively). The implementation of the measure is supposed to lead to a saving in fuel consumption.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', 'Owing to achieved energy saving this measure results in reduction of contaminants generated by electricity generation, liek Nox, Sox, TSP, CO,&hellip;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(503, 'ES-AGR-06', NULL, '64', 'Increase of conserving sowing', 'Reduction of fuel consumption of agricultural tractors by promotion of conserving agriculture.', 'Within the techniques used in the agriculture sector a mode called conserving agriculture exists, which, besides other aspects, implies less sowing of soil for cultivation. This technique comprises less utilisation of agricultural machinery, which implies less emissions of CO2, NOx, SO2 and COVNM due to reduced fuel consumption of tractors. The potentially applicable cultivations for conserving agriculture are the following: cereals, sun flower, maiz, rapeseed, peas, garbanzo, beetroot, flax, cotton, grassland, olive, citrus fruit, pear, peach and grape.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The effect of this measure cannot be quantified independently of the rest, because of the interrelation of all considered in the projections.', 'Communication of Spain to the European Commission relative to greenhouse gas projections and effects of policies and measures in accordance with Decision 280/2004/EC. Attached template: ES 2007_Spain_Template_Decisions_280-2004_2005-166 (V.3.1)', 'Due to achieved fuel savings, this measure results in reduction of contaminants generated in motors of agricultural machinery, like Nox, Sox, TSP, CO,&hellip;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
