(1118, 'PT-WAM-02', NULL, 'MRr1', 'MRr1. Directive on Packaging and Packaging Waste', 'Recovery and recycling objectives for packaging waste. The targets, to be met by the 31st December 2012 are:<br />- recovery: of at least 60% of waste<br />- Recycling:<br />Overall: 55-80%<br />Glass: 60%<br />Paper: 60<br />Metals: 50%<br />Plastics: 22,5%<br />Wood: 15%', 'Decree-Law 366-A/97, of 20 December, transposed the EC Directives that manage the flow of packaging and related waste (Directive 94/62/CE of the European Parliament and Council, of 20 December, altered by Directive 2004/12/CE of the European Parliament and Council, of 11 February)', '1998', '2012', NULL, NULL, '900', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'NA', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PT Submission 07', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(1119, 'PT-WAM-03', NULL, 'MRr2', 'MRr2. Landfill Directive', 'Definition of a national strategy to reduce biodegradable municipal waste (BMW) destined to landfills. Maximum percentage of BMW disposed in landfills in relation to the BMW production in 1995 (targets): 2006 (75%); 2009 (50%); 2016 (35%)', 'Decree-Law 152/2002, of 23 May, transposed Directive 1999/31/CE of the Council, of 26 April, on the disposal of waste to landfills.', '2002', '2016', NULL, NULL, '363', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'NA', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PT Submission 07', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(1120, 'PT-WAM-04', NULL, 'MRr3', 'MRr3. IPPC Directive (Integrated Prevention and Pollution Control)', 'Improvement of environmental performance of facilities covered with regard to: discharges to the atmosphere, water and soil; waste production; use of raw materials, energy efficiency, noise, risk prevention and management, among others (Time Horizon: 2007-2010)', 'The IPPC Directive was transposed to internal legislation by Decree-Law 194/2000, of 21 August. Waste Management (Category 5) includes a set of activities of Annex I of DL 194/2000.', '2000', '2010', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PT Submission 07', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(1121, 'PT-ENS-12', 'CL-PT-ENS-01', 'MA2007e1', 'Renewable energies', 'Increase to 45% the goal of electricity generation in 2010 by renewable sources (previously 39%)', 'Wind Energy -Increase of the installed capacity goal in 1.950 MW , in 2012. New total of  5.100 MW with a 600 MW increase by equipment upgrading<br />Hydric Energy - Increase of the hidric potential through the reinforcement of the Picote, Bemposta and Alqueva dams production capacity: 575MW increase in order to totalize 5575MW of installed capacity in 2010 (National Dam Plan).<br />Biomass- Increase in 67% the installed capacity goal (100MW). Decentralized biomass power plant grid with 250MW of capacity<br />Solar Energy - Ensure good articulation with microgeneration goals and politics<br />Wave Energy - Increase of the installed capacity in 200 MW: exploring potential to 250MW in experimental projects in pilot &aacute;rea of S. Pedro de Moel<br />Biogas - Establish a goal of 100 MW of installed capacity in anaerobic waste treatment units (currently of 20 MW in 15 units).<br />Microgeneration - Program to instal 50.000 systems until 2010, with incentives to hot solar water in already built houses.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'CL-PT-ENS-01', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PT-subMM 07, p.22', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(1122, 'PT-ENS-13', 'CL-PT-ENS-01', 'MA2007e2', 'Operational start of new natural gas combined power plants', '2160 MW in 2006 will now be 5360 MW in 2010', 'Decommissioning<br />2008 &ndash; 400 MW (aprox.) 2 groups of old Carregado power plant, and of groups 3 and 4 of Tunes Power Plant<br />2010: Shut down of the fuel Barreiro power plant, and zero operational labor of the remaining fuel power plants<br />After 2010 &ndash; Shutdown of all remaining fueloil power plants', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'CL-PT-ENS-01', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PT-subMM 07, p.22', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(1123, 'PT-ENS-14', 'CL-PT-ENS-01', 'MA2007e3', 'Subsitution of coal in thermic power plants', '5-10% substitution of coal in Sines and Pego thermic power plants by biomass or watse resultant fuels', 'Energetic Efficiency &ndash; until 2015 will be implemented energetic efficiency measures to 10% of the energetic consumption<br />Low Consumption Lamps &ndash; fiscal differentiation', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'CL-PT-ENS-01', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PT-subMM 07, p.22', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
